{{Quote|Ever seen a Bothan well-spider? They fight like you. They fire strands of caustic silk out of their burrows at predators. I couldn't help but be reminded. That and the gangly legs.|[[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]], to [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]]|<ref name="Bloodlines">''[[Legacy of the Force: Bloodlines]]''</ref>}}
The '''Bothan well-spider''' was a gangly-[[Limb/Legends|legged]] [[Spider/Legends|arachnid]] that fired strands of caustic [[Silk/Legends|silk]] out of its burrows at predators. It shared its name with the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Species/Legends|species]].

